casebody.data:
David Anthony STEBBINS, petitioner,
v.
MICROSOFT CORPORATION. No. 13-8563. Supreme Court of the United States March 24, 2014.

Case below, 520 Fed.Appx. 589.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied.

The CHIEF JUSTICE took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
